Ensure that the following line appears in the filetypedetect augroup in the
filetype.vim in your .vim directory (i.e. ~/.vim/filetype.vim ) e.g.

augroup filetypedetect
  au! BufNewFile,BufRead *.lst          setfiletype pcgenlst
augroup END

Then place the pcgenlst.vim file in the syntax subdir

~/.vim/syntax/pcgenlst.vim

see :help syn-files for further details
